Sentencas: By compositing cerium oxide (Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95, GDC) with the dysprosium-zirconium co-doped bismuth oxide (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3, or DZSB, a novel DZSB-GDC composite electrolyte is developed, which has excellent sintering ability and ionic conductivity.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Reverse coprecipitation is used to prepare nano composite electrolyte powders, and the sintering and electrical properties with varying DZSB composite ratio are examined.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: After sintered at 1200 degrees C for 10 h, all composite electrolyte pellets can achieve densities of more than 95 %.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, as the DZSB ratio increases, the densification rate increases and the starting temperature of the densification stage decreases.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: 10DZSB-GDC shows the highest conductivity (sigma t) and has an activation energy of 0.92 eV below 550 degrees C, which is 8.9 % lower than that of pure GDC.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 400 degrees C, the grain boundary conductivity of 10DZSB-GDC was 113.8 times that of pure GDC.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity of 10DZSB-GDC remain stable at 0.015 S cm- 1
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: at 600 degrees C for 4200 h without any decay.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The open-circuit voltage and peak power density of 10DZSB-GDC based cell are 0.914 V, and 441.1 mW cm- 2 at 750 degrees C, which is 1.1 and 2.1 times that of GDC-supported cells, respectively.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This indicates that 10DZSB-GDC is a promising electrolyte material for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Enhanced sintering ability and electrochemical performance of Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 composited with (Dy0.2Zr0.05Bi0.75)2O3 for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
